    {
      "id": "PopularPost123010",
      "post_content": "I remember I had a bully in public school, one day I got fed up with him and in a burst of rage did pretty much as the art shows, used him as a sled down a very steep hill, he never bothered me again (he didn't die, though he was likely mentally scarred for life, karma in action).\n  \n   \nAs for the effect, this is great, swing with your horde of small goblins, they block some, you sack them in response and pump up your other goblins. Giving all your creatures in a goblin deck semi [blood throne](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=blood throne )  vampire ability for 1CMC at common? YES PLZ! ",
      "posted_by": "Sironos",
