      "id": "PopularPost354343",
      "post_content": "While BastianQoU is correct, one point of interest: You can actually activate other abilities while activating an ability or casting a spell, if and only if they are mana abilities. It isn't often that you'll need to, but it can come up. If you have Black Lotus and nothing else on the field, you could put a Frogmite on the stack and affinity pays for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol), then crack the Lotus for the remaining ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol), for example. And I suppose it could matter with ordering triggered abilities. (A mana ability is any activated ability that is not a loyalty ability, or any triggered ability that triggers off another mana ability, if it does not target and can add mana to your mana pool. They don't use the stack and can't be responded to.)",
      "posted_by": "manaderp",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost354343\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">While BastianQoU is correct, one point of interest: You can actually activate other abilities while activating an ability or casting a spell, if and only if they are mana abilities. It isn't often that you'll need to, but it can come up. If you have Black Lotus and nothing else on the field, you could put a Frogmite on the stack and affinity pays for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/>, then crack the Lotus for the remaining <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/>, for example. And I suppose it could matter with ordering triggered abilities. (A mana ability is any activated ability that is not a loyalty ability, or any triggered ability that triggers off another mana ability, if it does not target and can add mana to your mana pool. They don't use the stack and can't be responded to.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '354343'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy103809\">manaderp</span>\r\n                                (12/12/2013 2:00:03 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n